OL,4,CPet abduction to be made new criminal
OL,5,Coffence in England
OL,6, Pet abduction is to be made a criminal
OL,7, offence in England after a rise in
OL,8, reported thefts during Covid lockdowns.
OL,10,FTheft of a pet is currently treated as
OL,11,Fa loss of an owner's property, but
OL,12,Fministers want a new law to acknowledge
OL,13,Fthe emotional distress it can cause.
OL,15,FThe proposal is one of a string of
OL,16,Frecommendations in a report by the pet
OL,17,Ftheft taskforce - set up to tackle an
OL,18,Fincrease in incidents during lockdown.
OL,20,FIt found that around 2,000 dogs were
OL,21,Freported stolen last year.
